"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-02-fans-evacuated-olympic-venue-lebron-james-allowed-stay-watch-21346109\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Orders to evacuate anOlympicvenue in Paris were not extended to American basketball legend LeBron James, who was allowed to stay and watch the beach volleyball beneath the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.374932675407629e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997634440028332, \"rank\": 0.00017105799011792012, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Play was suspended at the Paris Expo Porte de Versailles on Thursday evening and ticket holders told to leave as a storm began battering the French capital.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.552029078244336, \"rank\": 0.4137521461490233, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The weather began to turn during the second set of America's clash with China, with heavy rain and lightning forcing the authorities to suspend play and send fans home.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8009511308112298, \"rank\": 0.24488374718262254, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ladies and gentleman, this is an important safety announcement, due to the weather you must evacuate the venue,' a message read over the tannoy system.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Please remain calm as you make your way to the exit and follow instructions from security.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for your understanding.'\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Play was suspended for over an hour as Olympic organisers waited for the storm to pass and got the court back into suitable condition.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A weather warning also caused the hockey Olympic venue to be evacuated on Wednesday, thoughfans did not react too well to the organisers' decision.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The remainder of the Pool B beach volleyball clash was played behind closed doors, with only a few stewards and an all-time great basketball player inside the open-air arena for the rest of the match.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James and his family was seen cheering on Team USA when the stadium was full and they threw on cagoules to cope with the heavy and persistent rain.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.7006011859669281, \"rank\": 0.4264381767066109